Over the last 48 hours, a video clip of a Chinese employer appearing to assault a Kenyan employee has been doing rounds on social and mainstream media. Media reports have indicated that the Chinese national has been assaulting the employee for coming to work late. KTN news interrogates that clip and other pieces of evidence asking crucial questions whose answers suggest there could be more than what the police are investigating or what the victim has told the media and police. It is turning out, that the video may have not been a case of assault but some big babies games at the restaurant; this even as the restaurant management claims there have been attempts by the former employee to extort the Chinese national